<h1>Tomato Soup and Grilled Cheese</h1>
    <p>Tomato soup and Grilled Cheese is my all time favorite food. It's super easy to make and very filling. Its a great comfort food if you are sick, a rainy day, or sad.</p>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Tomato</li>
    <li>Garlic</li>
    <li>onion</li>
    <li>Peppers</li>
    <li>olive oil</li>
    <li>Seasonings</li>
    <li>Chicken broth</li>
    <li>Heavy Cream</li>
    <li>Cheese</li>
</ul>
<h2>Instructions</h2>
<ol>
<li>Roast all your vegetables top, with olive oil and seasonings</li>
<li>Blend with chicken broth till smooth</li>
<li>Top with the cheese and heavy cream</li>
<li> Severd well with Grilled Cheese</li>
</ol>
